{"tid":2162890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駿洋邨僅交還2座 餘下3座仍做隔離營","createTime":"2020-08-18T10:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T15:29:39.000Z","uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"849c89e17b1129e4f9197222df08aa3388111dcf","tid":2162890,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"政府今日正式公佈，駿洋邨第1至3座，因疫情急速轉差，有必要繼續保留作檢疫中心，料本年年底才可交還予房委會，預計最快在2021年第2季初開始陸續入伙。至於已交還予房委會的2座大廈可於本月底陸續入伙，<span class=\"red\">即公屋住戶有機會與檢疫人士同邨居住至少4個月。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/4YKCIM7XFNFRXBWKKZREIDK4GE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2F4YKCIM7XFNFRXBWKKZREIDK4GE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=8d021626\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2F4YKCIM7XFNFRXBWKKZREIDK4GE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6dfec18c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/4YKCIM7XFNFRXBWKKZREIDK4GE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"06f40a318f141e6dca2f36fdcdf581319c3799fd","tid":2162890,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"92f5b27fd7ae4234d54ccfc9957254b7922eedcc","tid":2162890,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"abc4040f13fb2c4efe3395822e67bc82cf708955","tid":2162890,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:00:10.000Z